title: Crowd Chants ‘TRUMP! TRUMP! TRUMP!’ During Priebus, Bannon Panel At CPAC [VIDEO]
text:
TOP 5498679 
White House chief of staff Reince Priebus and chief strategist Steve Bannon took part in a panel discussion at the 2017 Conservative Political Action Conference Thursday. 
Priebus had noted that he “lived through” the shock experienced by much of the country during President Trump’s 2016 campaign. Donald Trump (Getty images) 
“You kept running into your neighbors and you kept running into people you knew,” the former RNC chairman stated. “And what did you hear? ‘Trump, Trump, Trump.'” 
Priebus’ repetition sparked something in the crowd, which immediately broke out into a last name POTUS cheer.
